properties.description: It contains an orthorectified raster mosaic of the Capital District of Bogotá, the Cerros Orientales and  part of the rural area of Bogotá of the localities of Ciudad Bolívar and Usme, corresponding to 75,000 hectares. It has 4 bands of the electromagnetic spectrum: Red, Green, Blue and Near Infrared, allowing to create a false color for forestry applications.
